        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Promoting Election Integrity by Proving Voter Identity Act</strong></p> <p>This bill addresses the casting of ballots in federal elections. Specifically, the bill requires individuals to provide proof of identification for absentee and in-person voting.</p>]]>
        </text>
